Object.Field: This project will create all the fact and dimension tables for "Health Tracking" Dashboard.
DROP TABLE DIM_APPOINTMENT CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE

CREATE TABLE DIM_APPOINTMENT ( APPOINTMENT_FORM_ID VARCHAR2 (30), APPOINTMENT_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), APPOINTMENT_STATUS VARCHAR2 ( 30 CHAR ), APPOINTMENT_TYPE VARCHAR2 ( 70 BYTE ), APPOINTMENT_REASON VARCHAR2 ( 500 BYTE ), APPOINTMENT_RESULT_TYPE NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), NOTIF_LEVEL VARCHAR2 ( 12 ), ROOT_ID VARCHAR2 ( 30 BYTE ), IS_FOLLOWED_UP NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), FOLLOW_ID NUMBER ( 10 ), PROVIDER_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ),
CONSTRAINT PK_DIM_APPOINTMENT PRIMARY KEY ( APPOINTMENT_ID ) ) NOLOGGING
DROP TABLE FACT_APPOINTMENT CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE
DROP TABLE DIM_HEIGHT_WEIGHT CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE

CREATE TABLE DIM_HEIGHT_WEIGHT ( ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ) PRIMARY KEY, HEIGHT_WEIGHT_FORM_ID VARCHAR2 ( 30 ), NOTIF_LEVEL VARCHAR2 ( 12 ), HEIGHT VARCHAR2 ( 40 ),
WEIGHT NUMBER ( 10, 2 ), LATEST_WEIGHT NUMBER ( 10, 2 ), LATEST_WEIGHT_DATE DATE, OLDEST_WEIGHT NUMBER ( 10, 2 ), OLDEST_WEIGHT_DATE DATE,
ROW_NUMBER NUMBER ( 10, 2 ), BMI NUMBER ( 10, 2 ), PROVIDER_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ) ) NOLOGGING

CREATE TABLE DIM_MEDICATION_HISTORY ( ID NUMBER ( 10 ) PRIMARY KEY, MEDICATION_HISTORY_FORM_ID VARCHAR2 ( 30 ),
BEGIN_DATE DATE, END_DATE DATE, EVENT_DATE DATE,
EFFECTIVENESS VARCHAR2 ( 3500 ), NOTIF_LEVEL VARCHAR2 ( 12 ),
AGE_AT_EVENT NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), AGE_RANGE VARCHAR2 ( 7 ), AGE_RANGE_SORT_ORDER NUMBER ( 2 ),
MEDICATION_NAME VARCHAR2 ( 72 ), MEDICATION_SUB_CATEGORY VARCHAR2 ( 64 ), MEDICATION_CATEGORY_TEXT VARCHAR2 ( 500 ), MEDICATION_TYPE_TEXT VARCHAR2 ( 22 ) ) NOLOGGING
DROP TABLE FACT_MEDICATION_HISTORY CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE

CREATE TABLE FACT_MEDICATION_HISTORY ( MH_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ),
CLIENT_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), PROGRAM_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), TIME_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), PROVIDER_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ),
AGE_AT_EVENT NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), AGE_RANGE VARCHAR2 ( 7 ), AGE_RANGE_SORT_ORDER NUMBER ( 2 ) ) NOLOGGING
DROP TABLE DIM_SEIZURE_ACTION_BEHAVE_DESC CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE

CREATE TABLE DIM_SEIZURE_ACTION_BEHAVE_DESC ( ID NUMBER ( 38, 0 ),
SEIZURE_ACTION_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), SEIZURE_ACTION_DESCRIPTION VARCHAR2 ( 500 BYTE ),
SEIZURE_BEHAVIOR_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), SEIZURE_BEHAVIOR_DESCRIPTION VARCHAR2 ( 500 BYTE ),
SEIZURE_DESCRIPTION_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), SEIZURE_DESC_DESCRIPTION VARCHAR2 ( 500 BYTE ),
CONSTRAINT PK_DIM_ACTION_BEHAVIOR_DESC PRIMARY KEY ( ID ) ) NOLOGGING
DROP TABLE DIM_SEIZURE_DETAILS CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE

CREATE TABLE DIM_SEIZURE_DETAILS ( SEIZURE_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), SEIZURE_FORM_ID VARCHAR2 ( 30), DURATION_MIN NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), DURATION_SEC NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), NOTIF_LEVEL VARCHAR2 ( 12 ), BEGIN_TIME_HOUR VARCHAR2 ( 3 ), BEGIN_TIME_MIN VARCHAR2 ( 3 ), BEGIN_TIME_AM_PM VARCHAR2 ( 3 ), BEGIN_TIME_24_HOUR NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), PROVIDER_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ),
CONSTRAINT PK_DIM_SEIZURE_DETAILS PRIMARY KEY ( SEIZURE_ID ) ) NOLOGGING
DROP TABLE FACT_SEIZURE CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE

CREATE TABLE FACT_SEIZURE ( SEIZURE_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), CLIENT_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), PROVIDER_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), PROGRAM_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), TIME_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), ACTION_BEHAVE_DESC_ID NUMBER ( 38, 0 ),
AGE_AT_EVENT NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), AGE_RANGE VARCHAR2 ( 7 ) , AGE_RANGE_SORT_ORDER NUMBER ( 2 ) ) NOLOGGING
DROP TABLE DIM_SKIN_WOUND CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE

CREATE TABLE DIM_SKIN_WOUND ( SKIN_WOUND_UNIQUE_ID NUMBER ( 38 ), SKIN_WOUND_FORM_ID VARCHAR2 (30),
WOUND_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), WOUND_TYPE VARCHAR2 ( 500 BYTE ),
WOUND_SIZE_LENGTH NUMBER ( 10, 2 ), WOUND_SIZE_WIDTH NUMBER ( 10, 2 ), WOUND_SIZE_DEPTH NUMBER ( 10, 2 ),
BODY_PART VARCHAR2 ( 500 BYTE ), IS_WOUND_INFECTED VARCHAR2 ( 15 CHAR ),
NOTIF_LEVEL VARCHAR2 ( 12 ), PROVIDER_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ),
CONSTRAINT PK_DIM_SKIN_WOUND PRIMARY KEY ( SKIN_WOUND_UNIQUE_ID ) ) NOLOGGING
DROP TABLE FACT_SKIN_WOUND CASCADE CONSTRAINTS PURGE

CREATE TABLE FACT_IE_BA ( PROVIDER_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), PROGRAM_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), CLIENT_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), TIME_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), BOWEL_AID_TYPE VARCHAR2 (64 BYTE),
AGE_AT_EVENT NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), AGE_RANGE VARCHAR2 ( 7 ) , AGE_RANGE_SORT_ORDER NUMBER ( 2 ) ) NOLOGGING

CREATE TABLE FACT_IE_FLUID (
PROVIDER_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), PROGRAM_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), CLIENT_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), TIME_ID NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), FLUID_TYPE VARCHAR2 (64 BYTE),
AGE_AT_EVENT NUMBER ( 10, 0 ), AGE_RANGE VARCHAR2 ( 7 ) , AGE_RANGE_SORT_ORDER NUMBER ( 2 ) ) NOLOGGING

CREATE TABLE FACT_IDF_DIAGNOSIS ( CLIENT_ID NUMBER ( 10 ), PROV_ID NUMBER ( 10 ) NOT NULL, TIME_KEY NUMBER ( 10 ), OVERSIGHT_PROV_ID NUMBER ( 10 ), CLIENT_UNIQUE_ID NUMBER ( 20 ), ID NUMBER ( 10 ), constraint FK_PROV_ID foreign key(prov_id) references dim_provider(id) ) partition by reference(FK_PROV_ID) NOLOGGING
